videos.headline: Jillian Brown secures UVA's overtime win
videos.description: Jillian Brown comes up clutch at the line as Virginia battles past Missouri in overtime 87-81.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Jillian Brown secures UVA's overtime win) 2023/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mizzou forces OT but falls to Virginia in ACC/SEC clash
videos.description: The Tigers' hot start fizzles out as Hayley Frank nets a few late free throws to extend the matchup, but the Cavaliers come out on top by the final whistle, 87-81.
